{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318870/extras/PizzaWay.gif?t=1707150020\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318870/extras/Story.png?t=1707150020\" /><br>After centuries of oblivion, a mysterious organization emerges from the past: its secret agents call themselves Pizza Spies!<br><br>Pizza Spies operate at a higher level than government agents and maintain total anonymity thanks to the use of biodegradable weapons and devices that cannot be detected by normal security checks. This makes Pizza Spies lethal and free to act in any circumstances, above all other jurisdictions.<br><br>Their purpose? Protecting the world\u2019s balance from any gastronomic dangers\u2026<br><br>Secret agent Ace Cook will reluctantly be recruited to complete a very delicate mission: stopping the terrible &quot;El Cocinero.&quot; This is the code name of a criminal Chef Saucier who, by carrying out a series of culinary attacks around the world, intends to become the greatest chef of all time\u2026<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318870/extras/Features.png?t=1707150020\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318870/extras/Pizza_Icon.png?t=1707150020\" />  From the makers of the noir-comedy adventure \u201cDetective Gallo\u201d comes an<strong> action-comedy</strong> adventure that parodies the spy genre by putting you in the shoes of the secret agent Ace Cook!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318870/extras/Pizza_Icon.png?t=1707150020\" />  Decide to act in <strong>Covert </strong>(stealth) or <strong>Overt </strong>(direct) <strong>Mode</strong>, solving problems in different ways and overcoming specific game sequences according to your style!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318870/extras/Ace-profile-AP-RUN-x-GIF-resized.gif?t=1707150020\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318870/extras/Ace-profile-BP-STEALTH-x-GIF-resized.gif?t=1707150020\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318870/extras/Pizza_Icon.png?t=1707150020\" />  Complete missions to acquire powerful <strong>Pizza Gadgets</strong> with which you\u2019ll unlock new ways of interacting with the scenarios!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318870/extras/Pizza_Icon.png?t=1707150020\" />  Explore a game world with over <strong>40 locations</strong> that can be fully visited by riding in the Pizza Way, the hi-tech vehicle Ace is equipped with!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318870/extras/Pizza_Icon.png?t=1707150020\" />  Test your moral code by making <strong>narrative choices</strong> that will influence the course of events!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318870/extras/Pizza_Icon.png?t=1707150020\" />  Replayable adventure with <strong>multiple endings</strong>!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318870/extras/Pizza_Icon.png?t=1707150020\" />  Fully hand-drawn and animated <strong>cartoon-style</strong> exploration and action sequences!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318870/extras/Pizza_Icon.png?t=1707150020\" />  Original soundtrack and <strong>full English voice-overs</strong> (with Italian and German subtitles)!","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/ste